snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' TWIDDLEFINGER - All Endings (FNF Mod: TWIDDLE FINGER) Gegagedigedagedago Nugget
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' TWIDDLEFINGER | Max VS Gegagedigedagedago Chicken Nugget for the PC in 2160p Ultra HD. This time we play as the Chicken Nugget meme vs max. maxprolover988 - Created mod: https://www.youtube.com/@maxprolover988

👉 In this video I will show a guide on how to get the 2 different endings in this game. I'll be playing all of the TWIDDLEFINGER songs on very hard.

Friday Night Funkin': Twiddlefinger is a wild and quirky mod that flips the classic rhythm game on its head. In this mod, you play as the coveted chicken nugget, desperately trying to escape the clutches of Max, an evil monkey who is madly in love with you and will stop at nothing to keep you.

TWIDDLEFINGER Official Mod
https://gamebanana.com/mods/525021
--------------------------------------------------------------
► Disclaimer: This video is intended for viewers aged 13+ and older.
--------------------------------------------------------------

00:50 Turns evil

02:45 Lyrics (Good path)
03:45 Good Ending
04:17 Help Me, but I don't click
04:34 Lyrics (Bad path)
04:56 Bad Ending
06:01 Game Over
06:08 Outro - CommunityGame
